            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the aubergine is browning, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and your <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>chipotle stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1632303057745-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1632303057745-x400.jpg",
