            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the <strong>stone[s]</strong></p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and dice roughly</p><p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Crumble your<strong> feta</strong> into large pieces using your hands</p><p>Cut your<strong> lime[s]</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
