          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>diced avocado</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>and<strong> crumbled feta</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Add the<strong> </strong>juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lime </strong>and stir it all together – this is your<strong> feta & avo salsa</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into wedges</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
