          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine is cooked, shred it apart using two forks – this technique is known as 'pulling'</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>aubergine chilli</strong></p>",
