    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>aubergine chilli </strong>with the <strong>brown rice</strong> and<strong> feta & avo salsa </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
